node.text:
Always making sure our Loacker Minis are well stocked up at home because we snack and use them so often 🏠⁣
⁣
⁣ 😋The happy smiles whenever I managed to “bribe” my boys with minis. 🎲Giving our minis as rewards whenever we play family games together so the boys will play it with lots of patience! 🍱 Can’t wait to pack these yummy minis into their snack box when school reopen 💯✨👍🏻💖 💻For me, I’ll always have the minis around me whenever I’m getting some work done so as to destress myself. #dontwannasmashmycomputer⁣
⁣
What is your favorite ways of using Loacker Minis at home? Share and comment below ⬇️ ⁣
#StayHome #Loacker #LoackerSg #PureGoodness #Minis #Napolitaner #Creamkakao #Wafers #igsg #sgig #sgfaves⁣
